#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"                This module is designed to streamline your daily production, "
"from start to finish. It helps you manage customer relationships, prepare "
"for production, purchase raw materials, and handle deliveries. With this "
"complete solution, you\n"
"                can boost efficiency and improve customer satisfaction "
"across all your production services.\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"            Ce module est conçu pour rationaliser votre production "
"quotidienne, de A à Z. Il vous aide à gérer les relations clients, à "
"préparer la production, à acheter les matières premières et à gérer les "
"livraisons. Grâce à cette solution complète, vous pouvez améliorer votre "
"efficacité et la satisfaction client pour l'ensemble de vos services de "
"production.\n"
"        </span>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"                Welcome to the <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, "
"103);\">Odoo Textile Manufacturing</font></strong>!\n"
"            </span>\n"
"            <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"            Bienvenue dans le pack Odoo pour la <strong><font style=\"color: "
"rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Fabrication textile</font></strong> !\n"
"        </span>\n"
"        <br/>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"                When a purchase order for a subcontracted product is "
"created, the system handles the entire process. As long as your Bill of "
"Materials (BOM) is accurate, the purchase order will automatically trigger a "
"receipt for the final product\n"
"                and a replenishment order for all necessary components.\n"
"            </span>\n"
"            <span class=\"h2-fs\"><span class=\"h2-fs\"/></span><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"            Lorsqu'un bon de commande pour un produit sous-traité est créé, "
"le système gère l'ensemble du processus. Tant que votre nomenclature est "
"correcte, le bon de commande déclenchera automatiquement une réception pour "
"le produit final et un ordre de réapprovisionnement pour tous les composants "
"nécessaires.\n"
"        </span>\n"
"        <span class=\"h2-fs\"><span class=\"h2-fs\"/></span><br/>"

